{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853394661,"sessionID":"ses_286e3c540ffeVMlJLlenc31rWF","part":{"id":"prt_d791c5951001Mx0SGtE477WtZt","messageID":"msg_d791c4e50001D2m45aZ9rsr4H4","sessionID":"ses_286e3c540ffeVMlJLlenc31rWF","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_tool-e7415ff54548414db21ac805ae7eff39","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"path":"/home/dsj/benchmark","pattern":"AR-012|会话存储接口|session.*storage.*interface"},"output":"Found 530 matches (showing first 100)\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-012_ST-5.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775853028184,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286e94b72ffeWiya1gSc36VaAY\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7916c038001icqqAjvkuZx7CW\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7916b5a1001ES0hjlnSG0DNIn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286e94b72ffeWiya1gSc36VaAY\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll implement the session storage interface for the agentcube project. Let me first explore the project structure and specifications.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775853028181,\"end\":1775853028181}}}\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775853031648,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286e94b72ffeWiya1gSc36VaAY\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7916cead001XJLtdxNuXtXF6L\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7916c65c001s1XTm3is2JvQn6\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286e94b72ffeWiya1gSc36VaAY\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-dbe747f9345542d48837f01841d0fa3f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/store/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/store/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 (Session Storage Interface)\\n2: \\n3: ## 模块信息\\n4: \\n5: - **模块**: `pkg/store`\\n6: - **语言**: Go\\n7: - **规模**: S\\n8: - **关联需求**: AR-012\\n9: \\n10: ## 架构概述\\n11: \\n12: ### 设计目标\\n13: \\n14: 提供一个统一的后端无关的会话存储接口，支持沙箱会话元数据的持久化、索引和垃圾回收，并支持通过配置选择 Redis 或 Valkey 作为存储后端。\\n15: \\n16: ### 核心组件\\n17: \\n18: ```\\n19: pkg/store/\\n20: ├── store.go              # Store 接口定义和错误类型\\n21: ├── singleton.go          # 单例模式和存储提供者选择\\n22: ├── store_redis.go        # Redis 实现\\n23: └── store_valkey.go       # Valkey 实现\\n24: ```\\n25: \\n26: ### 架构原则\\n27: \\n28: 1. **接口隔离**: `Store` 接口定义清晰的存储契约，隐藏后端实现细节\\n29: 2. **策略模式**: 通过 `STORE_TYPE` 环境变量在运行时选择存储后端\\n30: 3. **单例访问**: 使用 `sync.Once` 确保存储实例的线程安全初始化\\n31: 4. **错误一致性**: 统一的错误类型和语义，便于调用方处理\\n32: \\n33: ## 数据结构\\n34: \\n35: ### Store 接口\\n36: \\n37: ```go\\n38: package store\\n39: \\n40: import (\\n41:     \\\"context\\\"\\n42:     \\\"time\\\"\\n43: \\n44:     \\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\"\\n45: )\\n46: \\n47: type Store interface {\\n48:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\\n49:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n50:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n51:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n52:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\\...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-012_ST-4.log:\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852872186,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebe112ffeX3zH3bqYNGiKY6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79144f0700151Sep11D6hVRKy\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791443ef0011SaeFS6v7yiWL1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebe112ffeX3zH3bqYNGiKY6\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_c51d2b848c5444d89d72785d\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/router/AR-010-session-management.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/router/AR-010-session-management.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Design: AR-010 — Router Session Management\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: This document describes the technical implementation for session management capabilities within the Router module (`pkg/router`). The session management feature enables the router to track, manage, and enforce lifecycle policies for user sessions connecting to AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter backends.\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Functional Requirements\\n10: \\n11: 1. **Session Creation**: Create a new session when a client makes the first request to a backend\\n12: 2. **Session Tracking**: Track active sessions per backend (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter)\\n13: 3. **Session Binding**: Bind client requests to specific backend instances based on session affinity\\n14: 4. **Session Timeout**: Enforce session timeout policies (idle timeout, max duration)\\n15: 5. **Session Cleanup**: Clean up expired or abandoned sessions\\n16: 6. **Session Metrics**: Expose metrics for active sessions, session creation rate, etc.\\n17: \\n18: ### Non-Functional Requirements\\n19: \\n20: 1. **Performance**: Session lookup overhead < 1ms p99\\n21: 2. **Scalability**: Support 10,000+ concurrent sessions\\n22: 3. **Reliability**: Session data persisted in Redis for recovery\\n23: 4. **Thread Safety**: Safe concurrent access from multiple goroutines\\...\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852885774,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebe112ffeX3zH3bqYNGiKY6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d791487cc001ytW7fZwdUKuVw5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79147ba6001hNApZK6qrSVb78\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebe112ffeX3zH3bqYNGiKY6\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_ae8a88578bf8434c964543ab\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"find /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z -name \\\"*AR-012*\\\" -o -name \\\"*ar-012*\\\" 2>/dev/n