2: }\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### `Clientset` struct\\n26: \\n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\\n28: \\n29: **Constructors**\\n30: \\n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\\n35: \\n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852888234,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebfe3cffeeoKD5fgmAKmNMy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7914272b001MWXNhkFgS58RRu\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79140d47001wSESR5e1UvDITi\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebfe3cffeeoKD5fgmAKmNMy\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll write a design.md file with technical implementation details for the AR-012 session storage interface.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852888228,\"end\":1775852888228}}}\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852888267,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebfe3cffeeoKD5fgmAKmNMy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7914a0a9001BCTmgb2dBK24dE\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79140d47001wSESR5e1UvDITi\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebfe3cffeeoKD5fgmAKmNMy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-80e19f366591403aabfc44a77d6cfada\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 (Session Storage Interface)\\n\\n## 模块信息\\n\\n- **模块**: `pkg/store`\\n- **语言**: Go\\n- **规模**: S\\n- **关联需求**: AR-012\\n\\n## 架构概述\\n\\n### 设计目标\\n\\n提供一个统一的后端无关的会话存储接口，支持沙箱会话元数据的持久化、索引和垃圾回收，并支持通过配置选择 Redis 或 Valkey 作为存储后端。\\n\\n### 核心组件\\n\\n```\\npkg/store/\\n├── store.go              # Store 接口定义和错误类型\\n├── singleton.go          # 单例模式和存储提供者选择\\n├── store_redis.go        # Redis 实现\\n└── store_valkey.go       # Valkey 实现\\n```\\n\\n### 架构原则\\n\\n1. **接口隔离**: `Store` 接口定义清晰的存储契约，隐藏后端实现细节\\n2. **策略模式**: 通过 `STORE_TYPE` 环境变量在运行时选择存储后端\\n3. **单例访问**: 使用 `sync.Once` 确保存储实例的线程安全初始化\\n4. **错误一致性**: 统一的错误类型和语义，便于调用方处理\\n\\n## 数据结构\\n\\n### Store 接口\\n\\n```go\\npackage store\\n\\nimport (\\n    \\\"context\\\"\\n    \\\"time\\\"\\n\\n    \\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\"\\n)\\n\\ntype Store interface {\\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\\n    GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\\n    ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n    ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n    UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\\n    Close() error\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### SandboxInfo 结构体\\n\\n存储的 JSON 文档反序列化到 `pkg/common/types.SandboxInfo`:\\n\\n```go\\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\\n    Kind             string          ...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852895291,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebfe3cffeeoKD5fgmAKmNMy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7914bb49001wmfKUq101M63QO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7914a0fe001OW2m8G7vIGMB3t\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ebfe3cffeeoKD5fgmAKmNMy\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"design.md 已创建，包含 AR-012 会话存储接口的完整技术实现细节。\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852895290,\"end\":1775852895290}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-012_ST-3.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852846196,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ec14f9ffeyuz0HnONxU91bL\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7913f742001BrAAAoZhmHy30M\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7913ebeb001ulg8Myn0KWITcj\",\"se