*: Pending\\n10: \\n11: ## Description\\n12: Define the session storage interface for the AgentCube project.\\n13: \\n14: ## Dependencies\\n15: None\\n16: \\n17: ## Related Changes\\n18: None\\n\\n(End of file - total 18 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\\n\\n## Metadata\\n- **AR**: AR-012\\n- **Title**: 会话存储接口定义\\n- **Module**: pkg/store\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: S\\n- **Status**: Pending\\n\\n## Description\\nDefine the session storage interface for the AgentCube project.\\n\\n## Dependencies\\nNone\\n\\n## Related Changes\\nNone\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-012/CHANGE.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852786037,\"end\":1775852786072}}}}\n  Line 27: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852794496,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7913325d001idzM4v342rrhK2\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791327c0001ippA85ivfqHqne\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-ace984b17fda4d038360418d068884b0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/session-store/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/session-store/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Session Store Specification\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: Persist sandbox metadata keyed by session id, index sessions by expiry and last activity for garbage collection, and support Redis or Valkey backends selected by configuration.\\n5: \\n6: ## Requirements\\n7: \\n8: ### Requirement: Store interface contract\\n9: The system SHALL provide a `Store` interface implemented by Redis and Valkey providers with methods: `Ping`, `GetSandboxBySessionID`, `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `ListExpiredSandboxes`, `ListInactiveSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`, and `Close`.\\n10: \\n11: #### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\\n12: - **GIVEN** a healthy Redis/Valkey server\\n13: - **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\\n14: - **THEN** the implementation issues PING and requires string response `PONG`\\n15: \\n16: ### Requirement: Not found semantics\\n17: The system SHALL return package error `ErrNotFound` (message `store: not found`) when a session key is absent on read or when last-activity update targets a missing session.\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: Get missing session\\n20: - **GIVEN** no key `session:{id}` in backend\\n21: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID` runs\\n22: - **THEN** error is `ErrNotFound` (Redis: `Nil`; Valkey: `IsValkeyNil`)\\n23: \\n24: ### Requirement: Session key naming\\n25: The system SHALL use string prefix...\n  Line 31: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852841199,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79134c59001SpX9MgWrNqjthM\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791332b6001pmTky27Bv8STnk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I'll create the delta-spec.md for AR-012 in the correct location:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852841196,\"end\":1775852841196}}}\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852841290,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7913e8f0001tGbn0vH233AsPa\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791332b6001pmTky27Bv8STnk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-cdf0d200c9aa43cea8fda5d2a067e4b0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-012 Delta-Spec\\n\\n## Purpose\\nDefine the session storage interface for the AgentCube project, providing a unified Store interface implemented by Redis and Valkey providers for persisting sandbox metadata, indexing sessions by expiry and last activity for garbage collection.\\n\\n## Base Specs\\n- deployment/client-go.md: Kubernetes client library for runtime API types (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\\n- session-store/design.md: Session store design including Store interface, Redis/Valkey implementations, and key patterns\\n- session-store/spec.md: Session store specification with detailed requirements and scenarios\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Store interface contract\\nThe system SHALL provide a `Store` interface implemented by Redis and Valkey providers with methods: `Ping`, `GetSandboxBySessionID`, `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `ListExpiredSandboxes`, `ListInactiveSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`, and `Close`.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\\n- **GIVEN** a healthy Redis/Valkey server\\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\\n- **THEN** the implementation issues PING and requires string response `PONG`\\n\\n#### Scenario: GetSandboxBySessionID retrieves session data\\n- **GIVEN** a session key `session:abc` exists with sandbox JSON data\\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \\\"abc\\\")` is called\\n- **THEN** it returns `*types.SandboxInfo` unmarshaled from the stored JSON\\n\\n#### Scenario: StoreSandbox persists new session\\n- **GIVEN** a valid `SandboxInfo` with non-zero `ExpiresAt`\\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\\n- **THEN** it executes SETNX ...\n  Line 35: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852845451,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7913f719001zMWxo1Y6BVyfpz\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7913e97d001YgjcLLMnILDav7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created delta-spec.md for AR-012 with all requirements and scenarios in GIVEN/WHEN/THEN format, covering the Store interface, Redis/Valkey implementations, key patterns, indexing, error handling, and provider configuration.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852845450,\"end\":1775852845450}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/resul