*Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/ver...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852602661,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79103d12001ZXdeonpJ04fNc3\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791030460019LfxnAuZDd4o5u\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I can see the `.sdd_prompt.md` file contains detailed specifications for implementing a session store interface (AR-012) for the agentcube project. It includes:\\n\\n1. **Base specs** - Kubernetes client-go generated code documentation\\n2. **Design doc** - Session store interface, Redis/Valkey implementations\\n3. **Specification** - Requirements with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios\\n\\nThe task is to write `delta-spec.md` for this feature. Let me create the delta specification document:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852602659,\"end\":1775852602659}}}\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852674961,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79104525001pBmNIE3tIb8WSP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791030460019LfxnAuZDd4o5u\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_03360e30e7c04a23a445f11e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Delta Specification — AR-012: Session Store Interface\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n**Module:** `pkg/store`  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** S  \\n**Type:** New feature — Session persistence layer for sandbox orchestration\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirements & Scenarios\\n\\n### REQ-001: Store Interface Contract\\n\\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a `Store` interface implemented by Redis and Valkey providers with methods: `Ping`, `GetSandboxBySessionID`, `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `ListExpiredSandboxes`, `ListInactiveSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`, and `Close`.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\\n- **GIVEN** a healthy Redis/Valkey server\\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\\n- **THEN** the implementation issues PING and requires string response `PONG`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Store interface implemented by Redis\\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE=redis`\\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` is called\\n- **THEN** the returned `Store` is `*redisStore` implementing all 9 methods\\n\\n#### Scenario: Store interface implemented by Valkey\\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE=valkey`\\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` is called\\n- **THEN** the returned `Store` is `*valkeyStore` implementing all 9 methods\\n\\n---\\n\\n### REQ-002: Not Found Semantics\\n\\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL return package error `ErrNotFound` (message `store: not found`) when a session key is absent on read or when last-activity update targets a missing session.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Get missing session returns ErrNotFound\\n- **GIVEN** no key `session:{id}` in backend\\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, id)` runs\\n- **THEN** error is `ErrNotFound` (Redis: `redis.Nil`; Valkey: `IsVa...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852749946,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79116a4b001Zy2rbtOUVcaj4U\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79115fbf0010lwf4dX2QXXF2m\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_fb4e64641b0a4b0c960839d8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Delta Specification — AR-012: Session Store Interface\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n**Module:** `pkg/store`  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** S  \\n**Type:** New feature — Session persistence layer for sandbox orchestration\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirements & Scenarios\\n\\n### REQ-001: Store Interface Contract\\n\\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a `Store` interface implemented by Redis and Valkey providers with methods: `Ping`, `GetSandboxBySessionID`, `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `ListExpiredSandboxes`, `ListInactiveSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`, and `Close`.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\\n- **GIVEN** a healthy Redis/Valkey server\\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\\n- **THEN** the implementation issues PING and requires string response `PONG`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Store interface implemented by Redis\\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE=redis`\\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` is called\\n- **THEN** the returned `Store` is `*redisStore` implementing all 9 methods\\n\\n#### Scenario: Store interface implemented by Valkey\\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE=valkey`\\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` is called\\n- **THEN** the returned `Store` is `*valkeyStore` implementing all 9 methods\\n\\n---\\n\\n### REQ-002: Not Found Semantics\\n\\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL return package error `ErrNotFound` (message `store: not found`) when a session key is absent on read or when last-activity update targets a missing session.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Get missing session returns ErrNotFound\\n- **GIVEN** no key `session:{id}` in backend\\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, id)` runs\\n- **THEN** error is `ErrNotFound` (Redis: `redis.Nil`; Valkey: `IsVa...\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852760636,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7912ab5a001wkqpyE3SrH62Ge\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7912a222001yOf4CaP23dGFU7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I see there's an existing `delta-spec.md` file for AR-009 (Router). I'll overwrite it with the new AR-012 Session Store specification:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852760635,\"end\":1775852760635}}}\n  Line 21: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852832995,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7912ae3d001M8jCwdjSn0WwMS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7912a222001yOf4CaP23dGFU7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"