\"messageID\":\"msg_d7913c9150017HzAwW3w91Y5JK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286efe104ffee5TgU7J0piu7fM\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done! I've created `delta-spec.md` for AR-012 (Session Store Interface) with 14 requirements in OpenSpec format, each with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN acceptance scenarios covering:\\n\\n- Store interface contract (REQ-001)\\n- Not found semantics (REQ-002)\\n- Session key naming (REQ-003)\\n- Expiry index with sorted sets (REQ-004)\\n- Last-activity index (REQ-005)\\n- StoreSandbox atomicity & validation (REQ-006)\\n- UpdateSandbox semantics (REQ-007)\\n- DeleteSandboxBySessionID cleanup (REQ-008)\\n- List loaders tolerating missing keys (REQ-009)\\n- UpdateSessionLastActivity preconditions (REQ-010)\\n- Provider selection via STORE_TYPE (REQ-011)\\n- Redis environment & password policy (REQ-012)\\n- Valkey environment & options (REQ-013)\\n- Singleton access pattern (REQ-014)\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775852839529,\"end\":1775852839529}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-015_ST-3.log:\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852699948,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ee9b3dffesjGz3k6Rl1TiT0\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7911bdd40013gFgOwfY3cK96Z\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7911a824001On14rRU0Q5awy2\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ee9b3dffesjGz3k6Rl1TiT0\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_a88f2c5d1cae4e0592819fc5\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Proposal: AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\\n2: \\n3: ## Summary\\n4: \\n5: Implement Valkey storage backend for the `Store` interface in `pkg/store`, providing persistent sandbox metadata storage keyed by session ID with expiry and last-activity indexing for garbage collection. Valkey is a Redis fork with enhanced performance and features.\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: ### Background\\n10: \\n11: The agentcube system requires a Valkey-backed storage implementation for session management as an alternative to Redis. The `Store` interface was defined in AR-012; this AR implements the Valkey provider using `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`.\\n12: \\n13: ### Goal\\n14: \\n15: Implement `valkeyStore` in `pkg/store` with:\\n16: - Full `Store` interface implementation\\n17: - Sorted set indexes for expiry and last-activity tracking\\n18: - Multi-block atomic operations\\n19: - Configuration via environment variables\\n20: - Optional client optimization flags\\n21: \\n22: ### Value\\n23: - Production-ready Valkey backend for session storage\\n24: - Improved performance over Redis (enhanced Redis fork)\\n25: - Efficient session garbage collection via indexed queries\\n26: - Atomic operations ensuring data consistency\\n27: \\n28: ---\\n29: \\n30: ## Scope\\n31: \\n32: ### In-Scope\\n33: \\n34: | Deliverable | Description |\\n35: |-------------|-------------|\\n36: | `store_valkey.go` | Valkey store im...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z_logs/AR-011_ST-4.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852649428,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ef44c2ffenDTTydtMZC8npT\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7910f3e6001n8TRquUlsOd6V6\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7910d8c80018ek1BCcPDxEjRC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ef44c2ffenDTTydtMZC8npT\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-24a48f1f0d394dc0ab84038b7167a946\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |\\n6: |------|-------|\\n7: | AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\\n8: | Module | `pkg/router` |\\n9: | Language | Go |\\n10: | Size | M |\\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\\n12: \\n13: The Router JWT module provides token-based authentication for secure communication between Router and sandbox pods. It handles JWT token generation (signing), verification (validation), key management, and integration with the reverse proxy for Authorization header injection.\\n14: \\n15: ---\\n16: \\n17: ## Architecture\\n18: \\n19: ### System Context\\n20: \\n21: ```\\n22: ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\\n23: │   Client SDK    │────▶│     Router      │────▶│   Sandbox Pod   │\\n24: │ (Python/CLI)    │     │  (pkg/router)   │     │ (with picod)    │\\n25: └─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\\n26:                                │                         │\\n27:                                │                         │\\n28:                                ▼                         ▼\\n29:                          ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\\n30:                          │   JWT Manager   │     │   Kubernetes    │\\n31:                          │ (RS256 keys)    │     │   Secret Store  │\\n32:                          └─...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-012_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852656271,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286eef33bffeuDDJwDNP3Af82z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7911165a001hrySHdMq1uurnX\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79110d9f001q5s0hNXmgpq3Fc\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286eef33bffeuDDJwDNP3Af82z\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-7d5c9cd573c64d1a8fc5d5d151df88af\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\\n4: Module: pkg/store\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: S\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Clientset\\n15: \\n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\\n17: \\n18: ```go\\n19: type Interface interface {\\n20: \\tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\\n21: \\tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\\n22: }\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### `Clientset` struct\\n26: \\n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\\n28: \\n29: **Constructors**\\n30: \\n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\\n35: \\n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852689333,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286eef33bffeuDDJwDNP3Af82z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79119799001btWffnNZykcROm\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d791116c7001Z9AjRNleBgdOUl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286eef33bffeuDDJwDNP3Af82z\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-797c87a975e14e3da9927e2e9af79d7c\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n本提案定义了 `pkg/store` 包中的会话存储接口，用于持久化和管理沙箱元数据，支持按会话 ID 检索、按过期时间和最后活动时间索引以进行垃圾回收，并可通过配置选择 Redis 或 Valkey 后端实现。\\n\\n## 目的\\n\\n提供一个统一的存储接口来管理沙箱会话的生命周期，包括：\\n- 按会话 ID 存储和检索沙箱元数据\\n- 维护过期时间和最后活动时间的索引以支持高效的清理操作\\n- 支持多种后端实现（Redis 和 Valkey）以满足不同的部署场景\\n- 提供错误处理机制和原子性保证\\n\\n## 范围\\n\\n### 包结构\\n\\n```\\npkg/store/\\n├── store.go              # Store 接口定义和错误常量\\n├── singleton.go          # 单例模式和存储类型常量\\n├── store_redis.go        # Redis 后端实现\\n├── store_valkey.go       # Valkey 后端实现\\n└── types.go              # 数据类型定义（可选）\\n```\\n\\n### Store 接口定义\\n\\n```go\\ntype Store interface {\\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\\n    GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\\n    ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n    ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n    UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\\n    Close() error\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 存储的数据类型\\n\\n沙箱元数据存储为 JSON 文档，结构如下：\\n\\n```go\\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\\n    Kind             string              `json:\\\"kind\\\"`\\n    SandboxID        string              `json:\\\"sandboxId\\\"`\\n    SandboxNamespace string              `json:\\\"sandboxNamespace\\\"`\\n    Name             string              `json:\\\"name\\\"`\\n    EntryPoints      []SandboxEnt...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852752462,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286eef33bffeuDDJwDNP3Af82z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79128dfe0014QYK2mGE8cFJqg\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7911c469001BsDXdGC7VY1boF\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286eef33bffeuDDJwDNP3Af82z\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-a7eee454225b498eb8283477396c9554\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md\",\"newString\":\"- [HTTP Reverse Proxy Best Practices](https://www.nginx.com/resources/glossary/reverse-proxy/)\\n\\n---\\n\\n# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n定义 `pkg/store` 包中的会话存储接口，用于持久化和管理沙箱元数据。该接口支持按会话 ID 检索、按过期时间和最后活动时间索引以进行垃圾回收，并可通过配置选择 Redis 或 Valkey 后端实现。\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n为 AgentCube 平台提供统一的会话存储抽象，实现以下目标：\\n- 按会话 ID 存储和检索沙箱元数据\\n- 维护过期时间和最后活动时间的索引以支持高效的清理操作\\n- 支持多种后端实现（Redis 和 Valkey）以满足不同的部署场景\\n- 提供错误处理机制和原子性保证\\n\\n## Module\\n\\n`pkg/store`\\n\\n## Language\\n\\nGo 1.24\\n\\n## Size\\n\\nS\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **Store 接口定义**\\n   - `Ping` 方法：验证存储服务连通性\\n   - `GetSandboxBySessionID` 方法：按会话 ID 检索沙箱信息\\n   - `StoreSandbox` 方法：存储新的沙箱会话\\n   - `UpdateSandbox` 方法：更新现有沙箱信息\\n   - `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 方法：删除指定会话\\n   - `ListExpiredSandboxes` 方法：列出过期会话\\n   - `ListInactiveSandboxes` 方法：列出不活跃会话\\n   - `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 方法：更新会话最后活动时间\\n   - `Close` 方法：关闭存储连接\\n\\n2. **错误处理**\\n   - `ErrNotFound` 错误定义：会话不存在\\n   - 统一的错误返回机制\\n\\n3. **后端实现**\\n   - Redis 后端实现（`store_redis.go`）\\n   - Valkey 后端实现（`store_valkey.go`）\\n   - 通过 `STORE_TYPE` 环境变量选择后端\\n\\n4. **单例模式**\\n   - `Storage()` 函数提供全局存储实例\\n   - 使用 `sync.Once` 确保单次初始化\\n\\n5. **数据索引**\\n   - 过期索引（ZSET）：按过期时间排序\\n   - 最后活动索引（ZSET）：按最后活动时间排序\\n\\n### Out of Scope\\n\\n- 沙箱元数据的具体业务逻辑\\n- 跨会话的事务处理\\n- 数据库迁移和版本管理\\n- 高级查询和聚合功能\\n\\n## Impact Analysis\\n\\n### Components Impacted\\n\\n1. **Router 会话管理**\\n   - 使用 `GetSandboxBySessionID` 检索会话\\n   - 使用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 更新活动时间\\n   - 使用 `StoreSandbox` 创建新会话\\n\\n2. **WorkloadManager**\\n   - 使用 `ListExpiredSandboxes` 和 `ListInactiveSand...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775852759199,\"sessionID\":\