ckage\\n13: - [ ] Check error using `errors.IsNotFound(err)` instead of hardcoded false\\n14: - [ ] Add test case for Secret not found scenario\\n15: - [ ] Add test case for other Kubernetes API errors\\n16: \\n17: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTSecretNotFound` to verify error detection works correctly\\n18: \\n19: ---\\n20: \\n21: ### Task 2: Implement JWT authentication middleware\\n22: - [ ] Create `pkg/router/jwt_middleware.go` file\\n23: - [ ] Implement `jwtAuthMiddleware()` function accepting *JWTManager parameter\\n24: - [ ] Extract Authorization header from request\\n25: - [ ] Validate Bearer scheme in Authorization header\\n26: - [ ] Call JWTManager.ValidateToken() with extracted token\\n27: - [ ] Store session_id in Gin context on successful validation\\n28: - [ ] Return 401 Unauthorized with structured error on validation failure\\n29: - [ ] Add correlation ID logging for authentication failures\\n30: - [ ] Handle missing Authorization...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z_logs/AR-011_ST-3.log:\n  Line 37: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852613567,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79106f390014P9cRVukaaT7pq\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d790e698a0013qFam4L7dvOAC9\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-13bd8cfee6bf4627ae04742ac2c42eea\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Design\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n| Item | Value |\\n|------|-------|\\n| AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\\n| Language | Go |\\n| Size | M |\\n| Stage | ST-1 |\\n\\nThe Router JWT module provides token-based authentication for secure communication between Router and sandbox pods. It han