 in sandbox-orchestration `design.md`.\\n21: \\n22: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\\n23: \\n24: ### Store interface (exact signatures)\\n25: \\n26: ```go\\n27: package store\\n28: \\n29: import (\\n30:     \\\"context\\\"\\n31:     \\\"time\\\"\\n32: \\n33:     \\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\"\\n34: )\\n35: \\n36: type Store interface {\\n37:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\\n38:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n39:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n40:     Update...\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852277151,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f4eed9ffe5xOXE2nxjMMXP7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d790b4941001JCudttODOfrg7p\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d790b3631001bOCDBBqSOcDoGa\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f4eed9ffe5xOXE2nxjMMXP7\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_b9a278e49845426c946f84a3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/session-store/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/session-store/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Session Store Specification\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: Persist sandbox metadata keyed by session id, index sessions by expiry and last activity for garbage collection, and support Redis or Valkey backends selected by configuration.\\n5: \\n6: ## Requirements\\n7: \\n8: ### Requirement: Store interface contract\\n9: The system SHALL provide a `Store` interface implemented by Redis and Valkey providers with methods: `Ping`, `GetSandboxBySessionID`, `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `ListExpiredSandboxes`, `ListInactiveSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`, and `Close`.\\n10: \\n11: #### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\\n12: - **GIVEN** a healthy Redis/Valkey server\\n13: - **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\\n14: - **THEN** the implementation issues PING and requires string response `PONG`\\n15: \\n16: ### Requirement: Not found semantics\\n17: The system SHALL return package error `ErrNotFound` (message `store: not found`) when a session key is absent on read or when last-activity update targets a missing session.\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: Get missing session\\n20: - **GIVEN** no key `session:{id}` in backend\\n21: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID` runs\\n22: - **THEN** error is `ErrNotFound` (Redis: `Nil`; Valkey: `IsValkeyNil`)\\n23: \\n24: ### Requirement: Session key naming\\n25: The system SHALL use string prefix `s...\n  Line 47: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852323438,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f4eed9ffe5xOXE2nxjMMXP7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d790c004c001Hg412ZHLOnskR4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d790bea44001qlRPfZWc527ki7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f4eed9ffe5xOXE2nxjMMXP7\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"toolu_fa1986133c764e208f18ebf3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark\",\"pattern\":\"Zadd\\\\(\\\\)\"},\"output\":\"Found 54 matches\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-014_ST-4.log:\\n  Line 10: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_use\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1775852198127,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_286f62cb7ffeV3l1pQN8gI1KEf\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"prt_d790a0d270010GA7RHwnGiN0F6\\\",\\\"messageID\\\":\\\"msg_d7909fe62001gFGxCfz8XpbowW\\\",\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_286f62cb7ffeV3l1pQN8gI1KEf\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool\\\",\\\"tool\\\":\\\"read\\\",\\\"callID\\\":\\\"toolu_9ecd5db7066645988885764e\\\",\\\"state\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"input\\\":{\\\"filePath\\\":\\\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/store/store_valkey.go\\\"},\\\"output\\\":\\\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/store/store_valkey.go</path>\\\\n<type>file</type>\\\\n<content>\\\\n1: package store\\\\n2: \\\\n3: import (\\\\n4: \\\\t\\\\\\\"context\\\\\\\"\\\\n5: \\\\t\\\\\\\"encoding/json\\\\\\\"\\\\n6: \\\\t\\\\\\\"errors\\\\\\\"\\\\n7: \\\\t\\\\\\\"fmt\\\\\\\"\\\\n8: \\\\t\\\\\\\"os\\\\\\\"\\\\n9: \\\\t\\\\\\\"strings\\\\\\\"\\\\n10: \\\\t\\\\\\\"time\\\\\\\"\\\\n11: \\\\n12: \\\\t\\\\\\\"github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\\\\\\\"\\\\n13: \\\\t\\\\\\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\\\\\"\\\\n14: \\\\t\\\\\\\"k8s.io/klog/v2\\\\\\\"\\\\n15: )\\\\n16: \\\\n17: type valkeyStore struct {\\\\n18: \\\\tcli                  valkey.Client\\\\n19: \\\\tsessionPrefix        string\\\\n20: \\\\texpiryIndexKey       string\\\\n21: \\\\tlastActivityIndexKey string\\\\n22: }\\\\n23: \\\\n24: func newValkeyStore() (Store, error) {\\\\n25: \\\\topts, err := makeValkeyOptions()\\\\n26: \\\\tif err != nil {\\\\n27: \\\\t\\\\treturn nil, err\\\\n28: \\\\t}\\\\n29: \\\\n30: \\\\tcli, e...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z_logs/AR-011_ST-1.log:\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852182133,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7909cf4d001ZzMBL5GC6SkRZ9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7909b2a9001BzVssdQ4e7Q6pY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-1343ff9d890b413b9b4037897f06673e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-010/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-010/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Proposal\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Implement session management for the AgentCube Router component. This provides the core session resolution and sandbox creation logic that enables session-aware routing. The session management component:\\n6: \\n7: 1. **Session Resolution**: Reads `x-agentcube-session-id` header, looks up existing `SandboxInfo` from the Store when present\\n8: 2. **Sandbox Creation**: When session ID is empty, creates new sandboxes via Workload Manager HTTP API\\n9: 3. **Response Validation**: Parses `CreateSandboxResponse` from Workload Manager and builds in-memory `SandboxInfo` with session metadata\\n10: 4. **Store Integration**: Persists sandbox info to Store after successful creation for subsequent session lookups\\n11: 5. **Error Handling**: Maps Workload Manager errors to Router-specific error types (NotFound, Timeout, etc.)\\n12: 6. **Service Account Auth**: Attaches Kubernetes service account token for in-cluster Workload Manager authentication\\n13: \\n14: ## Scope\\n15: \\n16: ### In Scope\\n17: \\n18: | Deliverable | Description |\\n19: |-------------|-------------|\\n20: | `pkg/router/session_manager.go` | SessionManager interface implementation with GetSandboxBySession, createSandbox logic |\\n21: | `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go` | Unit tests for session resolution, sandbox ...\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852254757,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d790af5fd0018MMGAO0LQ0Y6KU\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7909fcc20010vktCFKLckYxyI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-eb97a8b624a7428e8efd3e3bdccca6cd\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Proposal\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nImplement JWT authentication and signing capabilities for the AgentCube Router module. This provides secure service-to-service communication and identity verification between Router and sandbox pods. The JWT component:\\n\\n1. **Token Generation**: Creates signed JWT tokens with RS256 algorithm containing session/sandbox identity claims\\n2. **Key Management**: Generates RSA key pairs (2048-bit) for signing and verification\\n3. **Token Claims**: Embeds session_id, sandbox_id, namespace, name as standard claims with 5-minute expiration\\n4. **Issuer Identity**: Sets `agentcube-router` as standard issuer for service identification\\n5. **Key Persistence**: Supports PEM encoding/decoding for Kubernetes Secret storage\\n6. **Public Key Distribution**: Provides GetPublicKey for downstream verification\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n| Deliverable | Description |\\n|-------------|-------------|\\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWTManager implementation with GenerateToken, key management, PEM encoding |\\n| `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | Unit tests for token generation, parsing, expiration, key encoding |\\n| `pkg/router/errors.go` | JWTSigningError type with APIStatus implementation |\\n| `pkg/router/doc.go` | JWTManagerInterface definition |\\n| RSA Key Generation | 2048-bit RSA keys for RS256 signing |\\n| Token Expiration | 5-minute default expiration (jwtExpiration constant) |\\n| PEM Encoding | encodePrivateKeyPEM, encodePublicKeyPEM, loadPrivateKeyPEM help...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-014_ST-4.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775852191271,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f62cb7ffeV3l1pQN8gI1KEf\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7909ee920012nHRB4dPD6IO58\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7909d4540014ltcRaSPTBPvvY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286f62cb7ffeV3l1pQN8gI1KEf\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_0ee79a4639874e37a85f81cf\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bail