R-012; this AR implements the Redis provider using `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`.\\n12: \\n13: ### Goal\\n14: \\n15: Implement `redisStore` in `pkg/store` with:\\n16: - Full `Store` interface implementation\\n17: - Sorted set indexes for expiry and last-activity tracking\\n18: - Pipeline-based atomic operations\\n19: - Configuration via environment variables\\n20: \\n21: ### Value\\n22: - Production-ready Redis backend for session storage\\n23: - Efficient session garbage collection via indexed queries\\n24: - Atomic operations ensuring data consistency\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ## Scope\\n29: \\n30: ### In-Scope\\n31: \\n32: | Deliverable | Description |\\n33: |-------------|-------------|\\n34: | `store_redis.go` | Redis store implementation |\\n35: | `redisStore` struct | Client, key prefixes, ZSET keys |\\n36: | `makeRedisOptions` | Parse REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD |\\n37: | All Store methods | Ping, GetSandboxBySessionID, Sto...\n  Line 21: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775851979555,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286fa1272ffeJLsxXpclIzkNF4\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d790663980018uHTDGc6XoL0PE\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79064baa0019WdeKdUJ4x3PjF\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286fa1272ffeJLsxXpclIzkNF4\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_fca2f0d5036240789dda36d9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nImplement Valkey storage backend for the `Store` interface in `pkg/store`, providing persistent sandbox metadata storage keyed by session ID with expiry and last-activity indexing for garbage collection. Valkey is a Redis fork with enhanced performance and features.\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n### Background\\n\\nThe agentcube system requires a Valkey-backed storage implementation for session management as an alternative to Redis. The `Store` interface was defined in AR-012; this AR implements the Valkey provider using `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`.\\n\\n### Goal\\n\\nImplement `valkeyStore` in `pkg/store` with:\\n- Full `Store` interface implementation\\n- Sorted set indexes for expiry and last-activity tracking\\n- Multi-block atomic operations\\n- Configuration via environment variables\\n- Optional client optimization flags\\n\\n### Value\\n- Production-ready Valkey backend for session storage\\n- Improved performance over Redis (enhanced Redis fork)\\n- Efficient session garbage collection via indexed queries\\n- Atomic operations ensuring data consistency\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In-Scope\\n\\n| Deliverable | Description |\\n|-------------|-------------|\\n| `store_valkey.go` | Valkey store implementation |\\n| `valkeyStore` struct | Client, key prefixes, ZSET keys |\\n| `makeValkeyOptions` | Parse VALKEY_ADDR, VALKEY_PASSWORD, VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE, VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE |\\n| All Store methods | Ping, GetSandboxBySessionID, StoreSandbox, UpdateSandbox, DeleteSandboxBySessionID, ListExpiredSandboxes, ListInactiveSandboxes, UpdateSessionLastActivity, Close |\\n\\n### Code Structure\\n\\n```\\npkg/store/\\n├── ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-014_ST-0.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775851904603,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286fa8444ffejf4udbdfHTo4K7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79059c2f001sQANbVCGmvJ45i\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79059472001Nt3M3ddslCilrR\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286fa8444ffejf4udbdfHTo4K7\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_5978d0f4f3724fd182d6f247\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"ls -la changes/\",\"description\":\"List changes directory contents\"},\"output\":\"total 60\\ndrwxr-xr-x 15 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:59 .\\ndrwxr-xr-x 16 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:14 ..\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 00:35 AR-001\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 00:51 AR-002\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 01:03 AR-003\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 01:21 AR-004\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 roo