oreType)\n47: \t\t\t}\n48: \t\t\treturn\n49: \t\t}()\n50: \t})\n51: \treturn err\n52: }\n53: \n54: func Storage() Store {\n55: \tif err := initStore(); err != nil {\n56: \t\tklog.Fatalf(\"init store failed: %v\", err)\n57: \t}\n58: \treturn storeInstance\n59: }\n60: \n61: func SetStore(s Store) {\n62: \tstoreInstance = s\n63: }\n64: \n65: type invalidStoreTypeError struct {\n66: \tstoreType string\n67: }\n68: \n69: func newInvalidStoreTypeError(storeType string) *invalidStoreTypeError {\n70: \treturn &invalidStoreTypeError{storeType: storeType}\n71: }\n72: \n73: func (e *invalidStoreTypeError) Error() string {\n74: \treturn \"invalid store type: \" + e.storeType\n75: }\n\n(End of file - total 75 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package store\n\nimport (\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"sync\"\n\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n)\n\nvar (\n\tstoreInstance Store\n\tinitStoreOnce sync.Once\n)\n\nfunc initStore() error {\n\tvar err error\n\tinitStoreOnce.Do(func() {\n\t\terr = func() (e error) {\n\t\t\tstoreType := os.Getenv(\"STORE_TYPE\")\n\t\t\tif storeType == \"\" {","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/store/singleton.go","time":{"start":1775853414610,"end":1775853414626}}}}
